---
title: Bacon and Butternut Risotto with parsley and Italian style cheese
description: This bacon and butternut squash risotto is a creamy and even decadent dish that's great if you're looking for something simple and satisfying. It might take a little bit longer to make, but from the very first bite, you'll see exactly why it's worth it.
